    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a focus on maritime operations, with the USS Gerald R. Ford operating in the Mediterranean Sea. Aircraft activity indicates a range of missions, including transport, ISR, training, patrol, and tanker operations. The data also highlights the importance of the Strait of Hormuz, with commercial transits at their lowest level since the start of Operation Epic Fury. Overall, the military activity patterns suggest a continued emphasis on maritime security and power projection, with a focus on the Mediterranean and Middle East regions.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
